Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这片寂静撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.34,0:00:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引领整个世界\N来到炽热之焰的最深处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.22,0:00:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灌注在朝天高举的愤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.76,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度点燃你的热情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.43,0:00:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸腾不已的火红热血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.87,0:00:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都已无法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.58,0:00:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.95,0:01:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍卫弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈阳超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无畏惧的向前奔驰吧\N直到冲过那深红色的终点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.91,0:01:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最后一刻燃尽一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了立花中尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.45,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠着你收集的资料\N地球应该能更确实的迈向胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下我们的计划\N也能更顺利的发展下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这张金卡代表着\N我们对你的感谢之意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“叹息的玫瑰念珠”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身体上没有任何异状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因为精神上极度疲劳\N还是请各位晚一点再会面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问你喔蒂卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让莉露小姐独处不会有问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不用担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她马上就会恢复吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露窥视到了外星异种的"记忆"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些情报量太大\N所以才会产生精神错乱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文是这么告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种(杰拉拜亚)的记忆是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论是雷文还是桑德曼\N一定还有些什么重要的事瞒着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们找各位找了好久\N少爷、小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐她不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.84,0:04:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天一大早就没看到她\N结果到她房间一看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌上只留下了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我突然不告而别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来隶属的单位\N正是EFA的情报部...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说吧\N我就是EFA派来的间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了盗取超重神的机密资料\N才隐瞒身份潜入城内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要EFA战力能增强的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星异种的战争\N也就能结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.84,0:05:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然相处时间很短\N不论如何我都很感谢各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了...\N和你们在一起我很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一定有什么地方搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他们有下达什么指示吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N他们说没有必要去追她回来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该早就通通知道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.83,0:05:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是莉露的事...\N就连绫香的事也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么重要的事都瞒着我们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暗中拿我们逗乐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不会是那样子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.58,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...我真是太不知分寸了\N我...我怎么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.75,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都明白的蝶雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.08,0:05:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐总是那么坚强\N也是我们大家所憧憬的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(北之塔的密码...帮我问候绫香喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湛蓝的海恬静的海滨...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的...好安静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来媚月真的是间谍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...到现在还没办法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和超重皇的停机坪好像哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道这是什么玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.25,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这种东西\N只要随便摸它个两下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.60,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在玩什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会是什么难道你...哎呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是立体虚拟影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.41,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会有身在水中的感觉\N但还是能呼吸和说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为这下死定了呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好险...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是哪里的海中映像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里的...会是哪儿呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎...怎么了?发生什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.97,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市被...太凄惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里...难道是...地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是...并不是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(本日破晓前)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(杰拉拜亚大量杀戮机系统)\N(自卫星轨道上...)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊?\N(展开了无差别攻击)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(使得机械城市遭到了致命性损害)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.73,0:08:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好凄惨...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...海洋吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.94,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰比亚斯的海洋污染\N已经到达极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不撤离的话\N我们就只有全灭一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰比亚斯的那些家伙\N还想要来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们瑟力亚斯光是为了维持现状\N就已经精疲力竭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法再接受更多移民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.39,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们老早就逃到开拓星球\N居然还有脸对留守者见死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们故意这么晚来\N是想夺走我们辛苦建设的成果吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位请稍安勿躁\N先看看这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是桑德曼耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用我们正在开发中的创星机...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用超重∑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说是瑟力亚斯星的开发\N就连兰比亚斯的污染也能够终止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太愚蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纸上谈兵的空谈就免了吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是连找个驾驶员都有问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰拉拜亚博士\N您的大舅子好像还没认清事实嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这表示桑德曼和外星异种...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是从外星来的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来杰拉拜亚(外星异种)\N是取自别人的名字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然桑德曼是杰拉拜亚的大舅子\N这么说来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是莉露.杰拉拜亚的\N亲戚之类的啰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼! 桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...是我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.34,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争似乎...已经无法避免了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到我们的创星机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到超重∑...\N连星球都能创造的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的想法应该就会改变才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说对吧雷文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星球正要灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去只有进行屠杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那也算是正义的话那我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以完全自主行动的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制会对目标地点赶尽杀绝\N的"大量杀戮机系统"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.04,0:11:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真的认为有必要用这种机械吗?\N修纪大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样兰比亚斯数十亿的生命\N将能因此得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为会自然分解\N所以也不会造成污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为此而牺牲瑟力亚斯数万条生命\N我实在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果非得要流血的话\N还是流的越少越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不这么觉得吗?疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.07,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不弄脏自己的手\N连打倒的对手有多痛都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样根本是机械才有的行为模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是人类该用的手段!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.81,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在机械外壳下又何妨\N我们非得要继续活下去不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箭也已经射出去了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算硬碰硬我也要阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.35,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连一个人都救不了的你\N又还能做些什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我妹妹...\N害露菲拉早死的人就是你疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果光会空谈理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却无法营造等质结果的话\N那就一点意义也没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重∑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创星机?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把控制装置给...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道...\N自己现在到底做了些什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不受控制的大量杀戮机系统\N将会开始失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说是瑟力亚斯了\N就连兰比亚斯上的一切生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会被赶尽杀绝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量杀戮机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠超重神的原型机...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人...人被压死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.79,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉原谅我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不应该...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不应该是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才和我分开妻子就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨着我的修纪.杰拉拜亚\N也死在瓦砾堆下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑟力亚斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰比亚斯的所有同胞们\N也全都死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我独自在这\N遥远的星球上苟活着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.59,0:16:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了时空?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.56,0:16:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据逃生艇航道\N进行自动追溯的结果判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是中途\N空间跳跃失败的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.53,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对她的主观时间来说\N就只是经过了数个月而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到这个新天地\N我的同胞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能活着真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人...就是莉露吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.83,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露.杰拉拜亚\N这是连她自己都忘掉的本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会失去记忆也是能理解的\N像这种痛苦的记忆...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露她...她知道了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不修纪.杰拉拜亚并没有\N告诉她我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他没让我知道\N莉露出生的事情一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.52,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她平静下来之后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算以父亲的身份和她相认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来莉露并不是孤独一个人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望她的精神能快点恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和外星异种的接触\N造成了她的记忆陆续恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她还处于精神不稳定的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想请诸位\N暂时先在一旁静静看护就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这包在我们身上吧对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.64,0:18:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今没告诉诸位一切真相\N都怪我太懦弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.51,0:18:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今之后还希望诸位能和我\N一同继续奋战下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是我一厢情愿的请求\N但拜托诸位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生才不会是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.86,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你主动拜托别人...\N感觉起来还真不像你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会让这颗星球\N也变成那样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连星球也能创造的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创星机是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很寂寞吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.67,0:19:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起打扰到你了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以到外面来了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为睡在房里的话\N就会一直做恶梦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.72,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我也想快点好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得心里好烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是要想起什么似的\N却又想不起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担心着我到底遗忘了什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙这里到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心吧莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看过这个\N你就能明白一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.54,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...修纪舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.72,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有个会去迎接你的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼自己也都不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.53,0:20:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼啊...\N莉露他就是你的爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂到底又怎么啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想要让她高兴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...你让她看了那些东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.21,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(希望你能把我当做你的亲人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅你在哪里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那家伙没来的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.07,0:21:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别碰她!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏减弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救护班快一点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.92,0:21:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.92,0:21:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就不会\N体谅一下别人的心情吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.36,0:21:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在让莉露看到那些画面\N她会怎么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.23,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不会多考虑一下吗?\N你这个机械混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.28,0:22:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因热恋而无法成眠的夜晚\N已经看腻了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.89,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想要听到人的声音\N所以随意打了电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.99,0:22:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了靠不住的语音留言\N你现在到底在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.74,0:22:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映着冰箱内的灯光\N我在狭小的宇宙里彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.78,0:22:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的唱片\N唱针已经跳开不知几次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信这不变的温度\N一直到什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.06,0:22:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边轻语嘛\N对让我听听你温柔的声音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.20,0:22:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们手牵着手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.97,0:23:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N浅浅呼吸笼罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.15,0:23:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边轻语嘛\N对让我听听你温柔的声音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.25,0:23:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们闭上双眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.32,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜进你梦里的\N甜美节奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.04,0:23:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的秘密终于揭开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这只是一场重大悲剧\N的序幕而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷\N请您打起精神来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.08,0:23:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家...爱娜不论发生什么事\N都会一直陪伴在您身旁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入沉睡中的莉露\N掉进悲恸之中的桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.88,0:23:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重骑警终于揭开面纱\N展露出骇人威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回“粉碎的女神(机组)”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会守护住斗牙少爷的!